sys	shannon_chat	PROCEDURE	JAVASCRIPT	mysql.sys@localhost	<modified>	<created>	INVOKER	
Description
-----------
ShannonBase Agent - intelligent SQL assistant embedded in ShannonBase.
Accepts a natural-language message and a conversation UUID; returns a
text answer.

Parameters
-----------
user_message    TEXT         Natural-language question or instruction.

Session configuration  (@chat_options JSON)
-----------
Set @chat_options before calling to customise behaviour.
All keys are optional; defaults are shown in parentheses.

Model settings:
  model_options.provider           VARCHAR   Remote LLM provider override
                                    (deepseek|dashscope|anthropic|qianfan).
  model_options.endpoint           VARCHAR   Custom API endpoint
  model_options.model_id           VARCHAR   LLM model ("Qwen3.5-2B-ONNX")
  model_options.api_key            VARCHAR   API key for remote provider
  model_options.temperature        FLOAT     Sampling temperature (0.25)
  model_options.max_tokens         INT       Max generation tokens (1200)
  model_options.top_p              FLOAT     Top-p sampling (0.95)
  model_options.repeat_penalty     FLOAT     Repeat penalty (1.1)
  model_options.frequency_penalty  FLOAT     Frequency penalty (0.0)
  model_options.presence_penalty   FLOAT     Presence penalty (0.0)
  model_options.deepseek_thinking  BOOL      Enable DeepSeek thinking mode
  model_options.reasoning_effort   VARCHAR   low|medium|high
  model_options.language           VARCHAR   Force output language (zh|en)
  model_options.timeout_ms         INT       Remote call timeout
  model_options.workspace_id       VARCHAR   Provider workspace/project id
  model_options.region             VARCHAR   Provider region
  model_options.api_config         JSON      Raw provider-specific passthrough

RAG settings (rag_options) — controls which knowledge base ML_RAG searches:
  rag_options.vector_store          JSON ARR  ["schema.table", ...]
  rag_options.schema                JSON ARR  Restrict auto-discovery
  rag_options.document_name         JSON ARR  Restrict to specific documents
  rag_options.exclude_vector_store  JSON ARR
  rag_options.exclude_document_name JSON ARR
  rag_options.vector_store_columns  JSON OBJ  Column name overrides
  rag_options.n_citations            INT       Citations retrieved (6)
  rag_options.distance_metric        VARCHAR   COSINE|DOT|EUCLIDEAN|L2
  rag_options.embed_model_id         VARCHAR   Embedding model
  rag_options.retrieval_options      JSON OBJ  {max_distance, percentage_distance, segment_overlap}
  rag_options.skip_generate          BOOL      1=retrieve only (default)

  NOTE (legacy): if rag_options is omitted, falls back to top-level
  retrieve_top_k / retrieval_options / embed_model_id / tables for
  backward compatibility with older @chat_options configs.

Budget / quality:
  plan_log_max_tokens INT   Max chars of query results passed to LLM (4000)
  summary_max_tokens  INT   Max tokens for summary LLM calls (2000)

History:
  conversation_id     VARCHAR  UUID for the conversation session. Omit to
                               auto-continue the last conversation on this
                               connection; set to "new" to force a fresh session.
  history_length      INT   Number of conversation turns to retain (3)
  schema_name         VARCHAR  Restrict schema-metadata lookups (DDL only)

Example
-----------
SET @chat_options = JSON_OBJECT("conversation_id", UUID());
CALL sys.shannon_chat("当前库有哪些表？");

SET @chat_options = JSON_MERGE_PATCH(@chat_options, JSON_OBJECT(
  "model_options", JSON_OBJECT("temperature", 0.5)
));
CALL sys.shannon_chat("后续问题");

SET @chat_options = JSON_MERGE_PATCH(@chat_options, JSON_OBJECT(
  "conversation_id", "new"
));
CALL sys.shannon_chat("换个话题的新问题");
	utf8mb4	utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci	utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
